Awak datang seorang? Mana yang lain?

631
00:53:19.238 --> 00:53:21.073 line:80%
Awak tahulah angin Yun-gyeong.

632
00:53:21.157 --> 00:53:25.870 line:80%
Dia takkan datang ke majlis si curang.
Kawan-kawan lain pun takkan datang.

633
00:53:25.953 --> 00:53:29.206 line:80%
Jong-chan ada lawatan kerja.
Yong-gu akan hadiri majlis resepsi.

634
00:53:29.832 --> 00:53:32.376 line:80%
Resepsi? Dasar si tak guna itu.

635
00:53:38.674 --> 00:53:40.593 line:80%
Wah. Siapa mereka?

636
00:53:42.053 --> 00:53:43.554 line:80%
Kawan pengantin perempuan?

637
00:54:06.786 --> 00:54:07.787 line:80%
Tahniah.

638
00:54:10.081 --> 00:54:12.833 line:80%
Saya rasa awak sendiri patut simpan.

639
00:54:16.253 --> 00:54:17.630 line:80%
Awak datang rupanya.

640
00:54:18.297 --> 00:54:19.298 line:80%
Cantiknya awak.

641
00:54:22.009 --> 00:54:24.303 line:80%
Tapi ini... Tak payah susah-susah.

642
00:54:26.180 --> 00:54:29.225 line:80%
Awak akan makan dulu sebelum balik, bukan?

643
00:54:37.525 --> 00:54:39.193 line:80%
Sekejap, itu...

644
00:54:40.569 --> 00:54:41.404 line:80%
Mari.

645
00:54:50.746 --> 00:54:52.915 line:80%
Saya rasa macam pernah nampak dia.

646
00:54:52.999 --> 00:54:55.459 line:80%
Itu bekas teman wanita awak? Kang Ji-won?

647
00:54:56.752 --> 00:54:58.295 line:80%
Apa? Dia cantik macam dewi.

648
00:55:00.423 --> 00:55:03.217 line:80%
Awak yang ditinggalkan, bukan?
Saya ingatkan sebaliknya.

649
00:55:03.300 --> 00:55:06.220 line:80%
Tak guna. Diamlah!

650
00:55:08.139 --> 00:55:09.348 line:80%
Menjengkelkan betul.

651
00:55:11.058 --> 00:55:13.060 line:80%
ADUAN

652
00:55:13.144 --> 00:55:14.645 line:80%
Apa ini?

653
00:55:17.314 --> 00:55:19.400 line:80%
Awak disaman? Awak ada pinjam wang?

654
00:55:30.953 --> 00:55:32.621 line:80%
Awak akan masuk sebentar lagi.

655
00:55:33.414 --> 00:55:34.415 line:80%
Baik.

656
00:55:40.337 --> 00:55:41.422 line:80%
Tak apa.

657
00:55:54.727 --> 00:55:56.187 line:80%
Kenapa awak lambat sangat?

658
00:55:56.771 --> 00:55:58.481 line:80%
Saya ingatkan awak takkan datang.

659
00:56:22.421 --> 00:56:24.423 line:80%
Awak sambut jambangan bunga saya.

660
00:56:25.800 --> 00:56:27.093 line:80%
Apa?

661
00:56:30.054 --> 00:56:32.640 line:80%
Aduhai. Awak mahu jambangan bunga?
Mana boleh.

662
00:56:33.516 --> 00:56:36.268 line:80%
Ibu bapa Min-hwan kenal muka awak.

663
00:56:38.437 --> 00:56:39.522 line:80%
Betul.

664
00:56:41.357 --> 00:56:43.025 line:80%
Gaun ini sesuai dengan awak.

665
00:56:47.613 --> 00:56:50.658 line:80%
Betul? Mak mentua saya yang pilihkan.

666
00:56:51.742 --> 00:56:56.080 line:80%
Ia agak mengecewakan,
tapi apa boleh buat? Orang tua suka.

667
00:56:56.163 --> 00:56:58.124 line:80%
Dia anggap saya macam anaknya.

668
00:57:01.877 --> 00:57:03.587 line:80%
Baguslah kamu berdua serasi.

669
00:57:06.674 --> 00:57:09.718 line:80%
Mari ambil gambar. Panggil jurugambar.

670
00:57:10.261 --> 00:57:11.137 line:80%
Tidak.

671
00:57:12.012 --> 00:57:14.557 line:80%
Saya rasa tak perlu pun.

672
00:57:24.692 --> 00:57:25.651 line:80%
Tahniah...

673
00:57:27.903 --> 00:57:29.530 line:80%
kerana kutip

674
00:57:31.824 --> 00:57:33.701 line:80%
sampah saya.

675
00:57:44.545 --> 00:57:46.505 line:80%
Park Min-hwan belikan ini untuk saya.

676
00:57:47.840 --> 00:57:53.053 line:80%
Jadi pakailah atau jual,
atau buat apa-apa yang awak suka.

677
00:58:12.031 --> 00:58:13.282 line:80%
Sampah?

678
00:58:14.283 --> 00:58:15.910 line:80%
Dia buang Min-hwan?

679
00:58:16.619 --> 00:58:18.621 line:80%
Celaka. Wah, barangan percuma.

680
00:58:19.914 --> 00:58:21.957 line:80%
Macam mana saya nak kerja di sana?

681
00:58:22.583 --> 00:58:25.252 line:80%
Tak. Tak mungkin.

682
00:58:25.753 --> 00:58:27.421 line:80%
Saya akan kahwini Min-hwan.

683
00:58:27.504 --> 00:58:29.381 line:80%
Saya akan berumah tangga.

684
00:58:29.465 --> 00:58:31.926 line:80%
Saya tak boleh terikat
pada awak selamanya.

685
00:58:33.302 --> 00:58:34.803 line:80%
Awak akan masuk selepas ini.

686
00:58:35.429 --> 00:58:38.807 line:80%
Tiba masanya kita berjumpa
pengantin perempuan yang jelita.

687
00:58:38.891 --> 00:58:40.267 line:80%
- Okey.
- Mari menyambutnya

688
00:58:40.351 --> 00:58:41.602 line:80%
dengan tepukan gemuruh.

689
00:58:41.685 --> 00:58:45.481 line:80%
Tak, saya merampasnya. Lelaki
dan keluarga yang dulunya milik Ji-won.

690
00:58:45.564 --> 00:58:46.941 line:80%
Semua dah jadi milik saya.

691
00:58:47.942 --> 00:58:49.860 line:80%
Saya menang.

692
00:58:50.444 --> 00:58:53.197 line:80%
Saya akan mula semula.

693
01:00:23.120 --> 01:00:26.790 line:80%
Pengantin lelaki, Park Min-hwan
dan pasangannya, Jeong Su-min,

694
01:00:26.874 --> 01:00:30.627 line:80%
hari ini akan berkahwin
di hadapan keluarga dan rakan-rakan...

695
01:00:55.194 --> 01:00:56.862 line:80%
Senyum sikit, puan.

696
01:00:57.363 --> 01:00:58.364 line:80%
Bagus.

697
01:01:00.657 --> 01:01:04.745 line:80%
Rupa Jeong Su-min
tak sama dengan maknya, bukan?

698
01:01:04.828 --> 01:01:06.455 line:80%
Mesti dia ikut rupa ayahnya.

699
01:01:07.498 --> 01:01:08.499 line:80%
Betul.

700
01:01:08.582 --> 01:01:10.084 line:80%
Saya ambil dua gambar lagi.

701
01:01:10.626 --> 01:01:14.004 line:80%
Senyum semua. Encik, senyum.

702
01:01:15.130 --> 01:01:17.049 line:80%
Nampaknya, awak belum jumpa dia.

703
01:01:18.884 --> 01:01:22.596 line:80%
Orang zaman sekarang upah tetamu.
Awak rasa dia diupah?

704
01:01:23.806 --> 01:01:24.807 line:80%
Aduhai.

705
01:01:25.474 --> 01:01:27.726 line:80%
Tapi kalau ingatan saya betul,

706
01:01:27.810 --> 01:01:30.479 line:80%
mak Jeong Su-min masih hidup.

707
01:01:32.648 --> 01:01:35.192 line:80%
Eun-ho, apa awak buat di sini?

708
01:01:35.275 --> 01:01:38.153 line:80%
Su-min hantar jemputan perkahwinannya.

709
01:01:42.449 --> 01:01:44.451 line:80%
Tapi masalahnya...

710
01:01:45.160 --> 01:01:48.831 line:80%
Boleh kawan-kawan
kedua-dua pengantin keluar sekarang?

711
01:01:57.798 --> 01:02:00.467 line:80%
Saya tunjukkan kepada Ye-ji

712
01:02:02.719 --> 01:02:05.180 line:80%
dan mereka datang dengan rupa begitu.

713
01:02:05.264 --> 01:02:06.265 line:80%
Sebentar!

714
01:02:06.974 --> 01:02:10.394 line:80%
- Kawan pengantin perempuan datang!
- Datang!

715
01:02:14.481 --> 01:02:17.568 line:80%
Mereka rasa bersalah
dan nak balas dendam untuk awak.

716
01:02:23.031 --> 01:02:24.241 line:80%
Itu kawan-kawan awak?

717
01:02:25.409 --> 01:02:26.410 line:80%
Tak...

718
01:02:27.453 --> 01:02:29.288 line:80%
Su-min, saya datang.

719
01:02:29.371 --> 01:02:31.582 line:80%
Siapa nak sambut jambangan bunga? Saya?

720
01:02:32.374 --> 01:02:34.793 line:80%
Mungkin Ji-won teman sejiwa awak,

721
01:02:34.877 --> 01:02:37.713 line:80%
tapi awak berkahwin
dengan teman lelakinya.

722
01:02:37.796 --> 01:02:40.382 line:80%
Macam mana dia boleh sambut untuk awak?

723
01:02:40.966 --> 01:02:42.342 line:80%
Benarkah?

724
01:02:42.843 --> 01:02:44.470 line:80%
Dia rampas teman lelaki kawannya?

725
01:02:46.972 --> 01:02:49.391 line:80%
Awak hantar jemputan kepada siapa lagi?

726
01:02:51.018 --> 01:02:52.102 line:80%
Uruskannya.

727
01:02:56.064 --> 01:02:57.900 line:80%
Apa yang kamu buat?

728
01:03:00.986 --> 01:03:02.446 line:80%
Siapa kamu semua?

729
01:03:03.947 --> 01:03:05.949 line:80%
- Saya patut sapa dia.
- Jangan...

730
01:03:08.160 --> 01:03:12.789 line:80%
Saya kawan baik Su-min. Si bola mata kiri!

731
01:03:14.374 --> 01:03:16.293 line:80%
Lepaskan saya.

732
01:03:16.376 --> 01:03:18.462 line:80%
Apa... Mana adab kamu?

733
01:03:19.004 --> 01:03:21.673 line:80%
Saya kawan baik yang satu lagi.
Si bola mata kanan.

734
01:03:21.757 --> 01:03:24.843 line:80%
Dari mana datangnya
orang-orang biadab begini?

735
01:03:27.179 --> 01:03:28.430 line:80%
Biadab?

736
01:03:28.514 --> 01:03:30.015 line:80%
Apa yang mak cik fikirkan?

737
01:03:31.391 --> 01:03:35.896 line:80%
Kami seperti bebola matanya.
Kami juga mata air untuk satu sama lain.

738
01:03:36.813 --> 01:03:39.900 line:80%
Jangan begitu.
Mak cik fikir tentang orang biadab?

739
01:03:39.983 --> 01:03:41.443 line:80%
Saya si hidung!

740
01:03:41.527 --> 01:03:44.738 line:80%
Mereka bebola mata kanan dan kiri
dan saya pula hidungnya.

741
01:03:45.614 --> 01:03:48.242 line:80%
Kamu tahu ini majlis perkahwinan
keluarga siapa?

742
01:03:48.825 --> 01:03:53.705 line:80%
Keluarga yang besarkan anjing yang
mencurangi kekasihnya dengan kawan baik.

743
01:03:54.373 --> 01:03:57.125 line:80%
Kalau ada lagi rahsia, beritahulah saya.

744
01:03:57.209 --> 01:03:59.419 line:80%
Apa kamu kata?

745
01:04:00.212 --> 01:04:01.213 line:80%
Berani kamu?

746
01:04:03.048 --> 01:04:04.883 line:80%
Berhenti! Mak!

747
01:04:06.760 --> 01:04:08.136 line:80%
Berani kamu!

748
01:04:09.930 --> 01:04:13.058 line:80%
- Mak!
- Halau mereka!

749
01:04:19.773 --> 01:04:21.567 line:80%
Di mana Min-hwan?

750
01:04:21.650 --> 01:04:24.027 line:80%
Bertenang, semua.

751
01:04:24.111 --> 01:04:25.862 line:80%
Tiada apa-apa yang berlaku.

752
01:04:26.446 --> 01:04:29.616 line:80%
Mari tamatkan majlis ini.
Di mana pengantin lelaki?

753
01:04:29.700 --> 01:04:30.701 line:80%
Min-hwan!

754
01:04:31.952 --> 01:04:33.453 line:80%
Hebatnya kawan-kawan awak.

755
01:04:34.913 --> 01:04:37.791 line:80%
Mereka pun hebat ketika mereka buli saya.

756
01:04:42.004 --> 01:04:43.672 line:80%
Kalau awak penat, boleh kita balik?

757
01:04:44.339 --> 01:04:45.382 line:80%
Jom?

758
01:04:46.008 --> 01:04:47.926 line:80%
Kamu berdua boleh bercakap nanti.

759
01:04:50.596 --> 01:04:52.848 line:80%
Ya, kamu berdua. Saya akan hubungi awak.

760
01:04:52.931 --> 01:04:54.766 line:80%
Baiklah.

761
01:04:54.850 --> 01:04:58.395 line:80%
Awak tak nak makan?
Saya dah bayar 1,000 untuk tiket makan.

762
01:05:00.147 --> 01:05:01.148 line:80%
Mari.

763
01:05:09.531 --> 01:05:11.241 line:80%
Mesti dia dah buat keputusan.

764
01:05:12.618 --> 01:05:13.619 line:80%
Awak tak apa-apa?

765
01:05:15.078 --> 01:05:17.748 line:80%
Saya nak pergi makan. Nak ikut tak?

766
01:05:20.042 --> 01:05:22.669 line:80%
Saya belanja jika awak
nak makan di tempat lain.

767
01:05:23.629 --> 01:05:25.422 line:80%
Mestilah! Boleh juga.

768
01:05:27.049 --> 01:05:32.220 line:80%
Tapi pengurus saya juga sepatutnya datang.

769
01:05:33.305 --> 01:05:34.389 line:80%
Di mana dia?

770
01:05:46.318 --> 01:05:48.278 line:80%
Saya dah kata, jangan kembali ke sini.

771
01:05:51.782 --> 01:05:53.867 line:80%
Ini hujung minggu. Kenapa datang?

772
01:05:58.789 --> 01:06:01.750 line:80%
Saya tak boleh balik sekarang.

773
01:06:05.587 --> 01:06:07.255 line:80%
Yeon-ji ada di rumah.

774
01:06:09.216 --> 01:06:13.053 line:80%
Saya sendiri pula belum bersedia.

775
01:06:16.515 --> 01:06:18.308 line:80%
Saya terlalu sibuk.

776
01:06:20.686 --> 01:06:24.648 line:80%
Jadi saya tak sempat
nak ketahui keputusan pemeriksaan.

777
01:06:27.984 --> 01:06:29.903 line:80%
Saya dapat tahu melalui telefon saja.

778
01:06:30.654 --> 01:06:33.073 line:80%
Bertenang dan cakap dengan jelas.

779
01:06:33.657 --> 01:06:34.658 line:80%
Tidak...

780
01:06:35.784 --> 01:06:37.327 line:80%
Mari keluar dari sini.

781
01:06:43.625 --> 01:06:44.960 line:80%
Saya hidap kanser perut.

782
01:07:37.220 --> 01:07:39.931 line:80%
Syabas. Pergilah berehat.

783
01:07:40.015 --> 01:07:41.057 line:80%
Awak pun sama.

784
01:07:54.738 --> 01:07:56.865 line:80%
Saya datang untuk bercakap sekejap.

785
01:07:59.993 --> 01:08:01.536 line:80%
Tapi rasa kekok pula.

786
01:08:09.211 --> 01:08:10.712 line:80%
Helo.

787
01:08:10.796 --> 01:08:12.964 line:80%
Saya tunang Yu Ji-hyuk.

788
01:08:16.635 --> 01:08:19.721 line:80%
Sekejap... Mungkin bekas tunang?

789
01:08:21.765 --> 01:08:24.184 line:80%
Memandangkan dia batalkan pertunangan itu.

790
01:08:25.018 --> 01:08:27.604 line:80%
Saya tak tahu pula
sebab ada perempuan lain.

791
01:09:01.721 --> 01:09:04.099 line:80%
Awak pernah dengar
yang saya dah berkahwin?

792
01:09:04.182 --> 01:09:07.769 line:80%
Apa perasaan apabila teman lelaki
berkahwin dengan kawan baik saya?

793
01:09:07.853 --> 01:09:10.230 line:80%
Apa kita nak buat?
Cik Yang hidap kanser perut.

794
01:09:10.313 --> 01:09:11.314 line:80%
Ini salah saya.

795
01:09:11.398 --> 01:09:13.483 line:80%
Takdir saya diserahkan kepada dia.

796
01:09:14.067 --> 01:09:15.986 line:80%
Saya tahu En. Yu baik orangnya.

797
01:09:16.069 --> 01:09:17.612 line:80%
Ini salah saya.

798
01:09:18.655 --> 01:09:19.656 line:80%
Park Min-hwan?

799
01:09:19.739 --> 01:09:21.950 line:80%
Dia tinggalkan Min-hwan pada saya

800
01:09:22.617 --> 01:09:24.452 line:80%
dan cari lelaki kaya?

801
01:09:26.997 --> 01:09:29.958 line:80%
Saya tak suka sesiapa
menyentuh hak milik saya.

802
01:09:30.041 --> 01:09:33.920 line:80%
Saya sedar saya impikan
sesuatu yang terlalu bahagia.

